---
title: Veggie Meatloaf with Beyond Meat®, Mash and BBQ Sauce
description: Who said meatloaf couldn't be luxurious? This week, we're giving this comfort classic a Beyond Meat® twist with a sweet BBQ glaze. There are mashed potatoes, sweet honey glazed carrots and peas for a comfort meets sophistication dinner.
